      • checkTags

        private int checkTags​(int numOfTags)
        Check to make sure that all fields are passed in correctly
        Parameters:
        numOfTags - how many tags are filled out properly (starting at top, one row at a time).
        Returns:
        0 on success -1 if tag/value pairs are not both filled out, -2 if rows are not filled in from top to bottom (e.g. row 4 has a tag/value pair, but row 1, 2, or 3 doesn't)
